iew, update, full access</li></ul></ul><li>Add / Update users</li><ul><li>User List</li><li>Enable / disable users</li></ul></ul>\r\n                                    <b>Integration’s</b>\r\n                                     <ul><li> SMS integration</li><li>Email integration</li></ul>\r\n                                    <b>Reports & other feature</b>\r\n                                     <ul><li>Customer List</li><li>Customer Report</li><ul><li>Customer / site wise analysis report</li><li>Monthly report</li><li>QTLY report</li><li>Yearly Report</li></ul></ul>\r\n                                   \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                        \r\n                    \r\n                \r\n                \r\n\r\n                  \r\n                \r\n                    \r\n                        \r\n                            \r\n                                \r\n                                    \r\n                                   \r\n                                  \r\n                                     \r\n                                    <center><p><b><u>WEB BASED CUSTOMER SITE (SUPERVISOR) PANEL</u></b></p></center>\r\n                                    <p><b><u>KEY MODULES:</u></b></p>\r\n                                    <p><b>Customer Site Setup</b></p>\r\n                                    <ul><li>Add / update rooms, desks, etc.</li><ul><li>Area / Location wise activity mapping</li></ul></ul>\r\n                                   \r\n                                    <ul><li>Activity (Task) management</li><ul><li>Add / update activities</li><li>Add / update schedules</li><ul><li>View, update, full access</li></ul></ul></ul>\r\n                                 \r\n\r\n                                     <b>Site Operations Management</b>\r\n                                    \r\n                                     <ul><li>Housekeeping Operations</li><ul><li>Attendance of staff</li><li>Assign scheduled tasks to user </li></ul><li>Cleaning / sensitization monitoring</li><ul><li>Provision to create QR \r\ncodes for all areas where Sanitization and Disinfection must be done \r\nfrequently (RFID based auto scanning solution optional)</li><li>Housekeeping person can \r\nscan respective QR codes while cleaning / Sanitization area, desk (RFID \r\nbased auto scanning solution optional)</li><li>On scanning QR auto update in system</li></ul><li>Easy to monitor cleaning / Sanitization status</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n                                    \r\n                                     <ul><li>Resource management</li><ul><li>Attendance</li><li>Assign activities </li></ul><li>Inventory Management</li><ul><li>Housekeeping inventory</li><li>Provision to set minimum QTY</li><li>Provision to update used items / goods</li><li>System will notify to respective user on low inventory</li></ul></ul><p></p>', '', '', 'Terms And Condition Design Final', '<p><b><u>TERMS & CONDITION:</u></b></p>\r\n                                    \r\n                                     <ul><li>GST extra as applicable. (@18%)</li><li>Payment Terms:</li><ul><li>40% in advance along with PO</li><li>40% on completion of 50% scope of work </li><li>20% on successful UAT </li></ul><li>Development duration 40 working days form the date of PO or advance amount.</li><li>Server cost will be charge separately on need basis.</li><li> If need to travel outside the Mumbai, customer will arrange the traveling cost &\r\n                                        accommodation & additional cost Rs. 4500/- per day per person</li><li> If third party API required, API & integration cost will be paid by client.</li><li> Free maintenance for three months, after that 15% AMC cost applicable.</li><li>Above milestone not considered testing period.</li><li>\r\n                                        <br></li><li> For any new CR cost will be applicable based on change request.</li><li>SMS, Payment gateway and other third party costs will be client responsibility</li><li> Client will provide all required images and contents in soft copy format.</li></ul><p></p>', '', 0, '2025-02-06 20:18:23', '2022-07-27 11:40:56', '1', '1'),
